t;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For applicants that live in or have a link to Australia, please see this &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.airtable.com/company/job-application-privacy-statement&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Privacy Collection Statement&lt;/a&gt; for details regarding Airtable&#39;s collection and use of personal data relating to the application and recruitment process.&lt;/p&gt;
