&lt;li&gt;Strong negotiation and contract management skills, with experience closing large, complex agreements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep experience collaborating with Sales, Customer Success, RevOps, BizTech, and Legal to drive customer retention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills, with the ability to forecast renewal outcomes and identify trends.&lt;/li&gt;
