&lt;p&gt;Our enterprise growth team is where we think about AI adoption for the largest orgs and how thousands of users interact with agents. We&#39;re hiring a product design manager to lead this team while staying close to the craft of design: you&#39;ll split your time between people leadership and hands-on design.&lt;/p&gt;
