&lt;li&gt;Know each person&#39;s growth edges. Give feedback that&#39;s specific, create stretch opportunities, and invest in their development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage resourcing for your area: scope work to match capacity, flag tradeoffs early, and protect your team from overload.&lt;/li&gt;
