&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years of product management experience with a track record of shipping products users love&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building AI/ML-powered features, or strong familiarity with LLM capabilities and constraints&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strong product instincts:&lt;/strong&gt; you can look at a flow and identify what&#39;s confusing, what&#39;s missing, what could be better&lt;/li&gt;
