&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills with demonstrated ability to make data-informed decisions quickly with imperfect information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills, with the ability to articulate a product vision and direction to both technical and non-technical audiences&lt;/li&gt;
